{
  "stem": "9878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what I want to bring in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It will probably be painful to a lot of people to listen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But please understand, I'm not trying to put a finger on anybody else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm trying to say, the murderers, people should know who is the murderer, and people should know who is the victim.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I tell you what I saw with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the [INAUDIBLE] was-- before the ghetto was formed, a big truck came with a big trailer truck, like I see on the highways.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Looks like a house, with blinds I never saw in my life before, because we use cotton [? foldings, ?] what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Covers in the windows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Blinds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is something special, America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw this truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the truck had red, big red crosses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first time in my life as a child, I saw German fraulein, blonde with red crosses hats on their heads, red crosses armbands here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they bend down from the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The truck stood there on the streets, and they asked for people who did not have any milk for their children, when the children are starving from hunger, they should go in the truck.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll take them to the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They'll feed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'll give them milk to drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they feed them, and they brink them back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Needless to say, did we ever thought-- I didn't even know from the beginning that this has happened, that the Germans are capable of making gas chambers on wheels, which now came out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There are many gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They did it to many towns, to many cities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The name of the-- of the cross, they put [INAUDIBLE] the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Women were standing, fighting to bring their children in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
